file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: Hello
  version: 0.0.0
servers:
  - url: "{server}:{port}/hello"
    variables:
      server:
        default: petstore.swagger.io
      port:
        default: "443"
paths:
  /hi:
    post:
      operationId: postHi
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema: {}
      responses:
        "202":
          description: Accepted
components: {}
